        <detaileddescription>
<para>Main function to call the user module example functions.</para><para>Main function to call the Load DDR Copy Image example function.</para><para>Main function to call the config secure communication function.</para><para>Main function to call the ExtractMetaheader example function.</para><para><simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS, if example is run successfully.</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE, in case of failure.</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
